Class SearchRequest.SearchTermsBuilder

  • Object
    • com.tozny.e3db.SearchRequest.SearchTermsBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    SearchRequest

    public static class SearchRequest.SearchTermsBuilder
extends Object
    Used to specify Search terms for a search operation

    This class must be used to construct a SearchTerms instance that will subsequently be used in a SearchRequest

    See the SearchTerms class for information about default values for each parameter.
